  schema:name "Aleem Zafar";
  schema:sameAs <http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/K2-6181>;
  schema:url <https://aleemzafar.com>;
  <http://www.ebu.ch/metadata/ontologies/ebucore/ebucore#hasAgentBiography> "Aleem Zafar is a Pakistani singer, artist, and creative strategist known for blending South Asian culture with global sounds. He began his musical journey in 2019 and gained recognition with songs like Rehna Yun, Raaste, and Mere Khuda. Featured in several media outlets, Aleem has over 4 million streams across platforms and serves as a brand ambassador for Sveston Watches. His track Raaste was nominated at the International Influencer Award 2025 in Bahrain."@en .

