  <http://www.ebu.ch/metadata/ontologies/ebucore/ebucore#hasAgentBiography> """The Brookside Music Association is a community-focused arts organization dedicated to presenting high-quality live music performances in an intimate and welcoming setting. With a programming vision that spans classical, world, and cross-cultural genres, the Association seeks to connect audiences with outstanding Canadian and international artists while fostering a deeper appreciation of diverse musical traditions.

Through thoughtfully curated concerts and special events, Brookside Music Association emphasizes artistic excellence, accessibility, and community engagement. Under the artistic direction of John French, the organization continues to expand its reach, offering enriching musical experiences that appeal to both seasoned concertgoers and new audiences alike."""@en;
  wikidata_property:\/P8860 "837063916" .

