capacoa:PrimaryActivity_agen a skos:Concept;
  skos:definition "You represent performing arts clients in contract negotiations, manage or organize their financial affairs, and generally promote their work"@en,
    "Vous represéntez vos clients dans la négociation des contrats, gèrez ou organisez leurs finances, et vous occupez habituellement de promouvoir leur travail"@fr;
  skos:hiddenLabel "agen";
  skos:inScheme capacoa:PrimaryActivity;
  skos:note "There are different types of agents: agents representing individual artists on the labour market and touring agents representing productions on the touring market. In economic classifications, they are the same. Do we need to treat differently for use cases in the performing arts?"@en;
  skos:prefLabel "representing performing artists, groups or companies"@en,
    "représentation d'artistes, de groupes ou de compagnies"@fr .

